  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/86f09072c67257a8630053977ca3041e.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow the Rhythm</h2>Follow the beat of different cities, with awesome city pop music and visual cues in the tiles on the floor. Also, master all the different kinds of floor tiles and solve the puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/789c1bfc5ae0192ab83230cd93a5e057.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pickup Souvenirs</h2>Collect all the souvenirs. These style the pigeon in cute and fashionable ways while also providing extra defense from enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/0b6060dfdab8f878e23a53e0cf2c269c.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid Enemies</h2>You’ll find all kinds of human enemies on your travels, with different behaviors and walking patterns. Although not malicious, by not noticing the pigeon and stepping on it, they can knock it down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.poster.avif?t=1741940878\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.webm?t=1741940878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.mp4?t=1741940878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move to the beat of city pop songs<br></li><li> Pick-up and collect souvenirs from around the world <br></li><li> Master all the different floor-tiles to solve puzzles<br></li><li> Avoid the enemies and move freely <br></li><li> Collect photos of memorable places in the world<br></li><li> Great with controller or in Steam Deck<br></li><li> Perfect for long or short play-sessions</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/5d1c86f98f2a5f8b70753cbb62d7c95c.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=158 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/86f09072c67257a8630053977ca3041e.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow the Rhythm</h2>Follow the beat of different cities, with awesome city pop music and visual cues in the tiles on the floor. Also, master all the different kinds of floor tiles and solve the puzzles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/789c1bfc5ae0192ab83230cd93a5e057.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pickup Souvenirs</h2>Collect all the souvenirs. These style the pigeon in cute and fashionable ways while also providing extra defense from enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/0b6060dfdab8f878e23a53e0cf2c269c.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=202 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Avoid Enemies</h2>You’ll find all kinds of human enemies on your travels, with different behaviors and walking patterns. Although not malicious, by not noticing the pigeon and stepping on it, they can knock it down.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.poster.avif?t=1741940878\" width=480 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.webm?t=1741940878\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/2aee5320f677f81a7e1c7dd41be4411c.mp4?t=1741940878\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Move to the beat of city pop songs<br></li><li> Pick-up and collect souvenirs from around the world <br></li><li> Master all the different floor-tiles to solve puzzles<br></li><li> Avoid the enemies and move freely <br></li><li> Collect photos of memorable places in the world<br></li><li> Great with controller or in Steam Deck<br></li><li> Perfect for long or short play-sessions</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2887950/extras/5d1c86f98f2a5f8b70753cbb62d7c95c.avif?t=1741940878\" width=634 height=158 /></span>",
